<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Zanzibar Escape</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: normal;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 0;
            color: #333;

        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 30px 25px;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0369A0 0%, #29BCB7 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;   /* Clips background to text */
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;  /* Makes text transparent to reveal gradient */
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;  /* Fallback */
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 60px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #0095c2;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #ff6b35;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .quote-box {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(171.9deg, #FFFFFF 29.33%, #E5F7FF 80.2%);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .quote-box img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .quote-box p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .quote-date {
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .quote-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            background-color: #003d9e;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .access-section {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .code {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #003d9e;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .copy-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0369A0 0%, #29BCB7 100%);
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .email-container {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRwJromFWFHBKmfdiQjQLo5iqIv8RLPJJKutA&s">
    </div>

    <h1 class="gradient-text">Welcome To Inibyte Limited</h1>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <span class="highlight"><%= username %></span>,</p>
        <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">Inibyte Limited!</span> We're excited to have you.</p>
        <p>To complete your registration and secure your account, please verify your email address using the code in button below</p>
    </div>

    <div class="access-section">
        <p><strong>6 Digit Code:</strong></p>
        <p class="code gradient-text"><%= code %></p>
        <a href="#" class="copy-btn" style="color: #ffffff">Copy</a>
        <p>This code is valid for the next <span class="highlight">5 minutes</span></p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p><span class="highlight">Didn't sign up for this?</span> If you didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email, and we won't bother you again.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions or would like to make changes, feel free to reply to this email or contact Inibyte Limited</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>
            Inibyte Limited</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
